Services Offered

• Certified Data Wiping: Software-based wiping using Blancco® following DIN 66399
standards.
• Physical Destruction: Crushing, shredding, and degaussing of storage media.
• IT Recycling & Disposal: Certified, environmentally sound (KrWG) recycling of
non-reusableequipment.
• IT Asset Refurbishment: Data sanitization and refurbishment for resale or
donation.
• Secure Software Disposal: Invalidation and destruction of licensed software
media.
• On-Site Services: Collection, destruction, and audit services performed at your
location.
